short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SpongeBob SquarePants wallpaper turn new tab to custom HD SpongeBob SquarePants background. SpongeBob background theme for fans.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension Features:

1. Every new tab surprises you with a different SpongeBob wallpaper.
2. Choose or favorite SpongeBob backgrounds from the wallpaper selection panel.
3. Integrated Google Search bar.
4. Direct links to your emails and social media profiles.
5. Automatically displays the current date and time.
6. New Note feature to jot down your tasks.
7. Quick links to your most frequented websites.
8. Convenient access to your bookmarks.
9. Shortcut panel for adding and accessing websites swiftly.
10. Immediate access to Google applications.
11. Easy access to additional themes.
12. Simple social media sharing options.
13. Instant download options for new wallpapers.
14. Quick links to games.
15. Enjoy interactive animations like snow, rain, falling leaves, and fireworks on your SpongeBob SquarePants new tab.
